title: message_offset()
brief: Get the current offset into the message.
seealso: index_offset, maildir_offset
version: 0.18
----

<p>When in message-mode a message will be displayed upon the screen.  The display consists of two parts:</p>
<ul>
<li>A list of headers (&amp; optionally a list of attachment-names).</li>
<li>The body of the email.</li>
</ul>
<p>The <span class="tt">message_offset()</span> function will return the number of lines the message has been scrolled down.</p>
